description: Liquid Nitrogen isn't just a way to dispose of a Terminator - it's also a great way to make ice cream! Using liquid N2 is a brand new way to make ice cream of your choice right in front of your eyes. No waiting for hours to freeze, instead you'll have your all natural, no artificial flavoring ice cream in mere minutes! Check out Liquid N2 Ice Cream for an amazing ice cream experience today!
name: Liquid N2 Ice Cream
